parts have to be present and functional at all times. Disorganization destroys
functionality.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Comments on Creation vs Evolution</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/evidences/creation-and-evolution/comments-on-creation-vs-evolution/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/evidences/creation-and-evolution/comments-on-creation-vs-evolution/</guid><description>&lt;style>
